# Backend Environment Configuration

## Development
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
LOG_LEVEL=debug

## GitHub Copilot Integration
# GitHub token with Copilot access for free AI model usage
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here

## Server Configuration
HOST=localhost

## Logging
LOG_LEVEL=debug

# File Upload
MAX_FILE_SIZE=500MB
UPLOAD_DIR=./temp/uploads

# Cost Tracking (Phase 3)
COST_TRACKING_ENABLED=true
COST_ALERT_THRESHOLD=1.00

# Video Processing
VIDEO_TIMEOUT_MINUTES=60
MAX_VIDEO_DURATION_HOURS=1
```

## Production Configuration
For production deployment on Railway/Heroku:
1. Use environment variables from platform dashboard
2. Set `NODE_ENV=production`
3. Use remote database/storage
4. Enable HTTPS only
5. Set appropriate cost thresholds
